Package com.versant.var.transport

Interface Summary
VARIEndPoint The interface used by the replication sender and receiver to get the input and output streams.
VARITransport This is the transport interface used by the replication sender and the receiver to get send and receive end points respectively.
 

Class Summary
VARDefaultEndPoint This is the TCP socket-based implementation of the end point interface used by the replication sender and receiver.
VARDefaultTransport This is the TCP socket-based implementation of the transport interface used by the replication sender and the receiver to get send and receive end points respectively.
